{
	"nodes":[
		{"id":"path-a","type":"text","text":"### Path A: Standard\n1. Static files in src/\n2. JFrog stores artifact\n3. S3 push component\n4. AWS OIDC auth\n5. s3 sync to bucket","x":200,"y":60,"width":200,"height":280,"color":"#f59e0b"},
		{"id":"repo-structure","type":"text","text":"### Repo: klm/app/source/\n\n**Vue.js SPA** (compiled)\n- app.*.js bundles\n- home.*.js route chunks\n- chunk-vendors.js\n\n**src/**\n- Private/ (auth area)\n- Public/ (login page)\n\n> Note: Only compiled output.\n> Source lives elsewhere.","x":-470,"y":120,"width":500,"height":360,"color":"#60A5FA"},
		{"id":"path-b","type":"text","text":"### Path B: CIFS Mount\n1. Vault retrieves secrets\n2. Custom runner mounts CIFS\n3. SMB to //cifs-frsel/klm\n4. AWS OIDC auth\n5. aws s3 sync /cifs/...","x":180,"y":360,"width":200,"height":333,"color":"#E07850"},
		{"id":"env-prd","type":"text","text":"### PRD Environment\nAccount: 737247133998\n\n`s3://hsi-kellymorphose-prd-frontend/`\n\nTrigger: Git Tag","x":620,"y":370,"width":200,"height":100,"color":"#16a34a"},
