		{"id":"phase1","type":"text","text":"### Phase 1: SETUP\n- init\n- build\n- sign\n- verify\n- manifest","x":-480,"y":-200,"width":220,"height":200,"color":"#E07850"},
		{"id":"variables","type":"text","text":"### Key Variables\n\n```yaml\nPUBLISH_REPOSITORY: artifactory\nGITGUARDIAN_FULL_SCAN: \"true\"\nDOCKER_TLS_CERTDIR: \"/certs\"\nGIT_SSL_NO_VERIFY: \"true\"\nDEV_ENABLED: \"false\"\nTST_ENABLED: \"false\"\nCHK_ENABLED: \"true\"\nACC_ENABLED: \"false\"\nS3_DEPLOY_IMAGE: docker-aws-cli-custom\nSMB_USER: svc_frsel_p_cisydep\nSMB_PATH: //cifs-frsel/klm\n```","x":-820,"y":80,"width":300,"height":500,"color":"#2D2D2D"},
		{"id":"custom-jobs","type":"text","text":"### Custom Jobs\n\n**get-secrets-rct**\n- Env: chk\n- Trigger: MR\n- Excludes: tags, releases\n\n**get-secrets-prd**\n- Env: prd\n- Trigger: Git tags\n\n**custom_s3-cifs:chk**\n- Tags: s3, cifs\n- Runner: docker-aws-cli-custom\n\n**custom_s3-cifs:prd**\n- Tags: s3, cifs\n- Manual approval","x":-1100,"y":-280,"width":240,"height":560,"color":"#2D2D2D"},
		{"id":"security","type":"text","text":"### Security Stack\n\n| Tool | Stage | Purpose |\n|------|-------|---------|\n| GitGuardian | init | Secret scanning |\n| SonarQube | analysis | Code quality |\n| Vault | init | Secrets |\n| JFrog | push | Artifacts |\n| AWS OIDC | deploy | No hardcoded keys |","x":-1220,"y":-670,"width":340,"height":360,"color":"#2D2D2D"},
		{"id":"env-matrix","type":"text","text":"### Environment Matrix\n\n| Env | Enabled | Trigger |\n|-----|---------|---------|\n| DEV | false | - |\n| TST | false | - |\n| CHK | true | MR |\n| ACC | false | - |\n| PRD | true | Git tag |","x":-1120,"y":320,"width":260,"height":300,"color":"#2D2D2D"},
		{"id":"baseline","type":"text","text":"### Base CI/CD\n**baseline-component**\n`baseline@~latest`\n\nProvides stages:\n- init\n- build\n- sign\n- verify\n- manifest\n- test\n- analysis\n- push\n- publish\n- schedule\n\nInputs:\nsonarqube_stage: analysis\nlanguage: unset\nlang_version: 1.20.0","x":-840,"y":-505,"width":300,"height":560,"color":"#E07850"}
	],
